{"id":534329334,"lang":"cpp","time":"3 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1628271291,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"468 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/534329334/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Remove Duplicates from Sorted Array","memory":"18.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int removeDuplicates(vector<int>& nums) {\n        \n        if(nums.empty())\n            return 0;\n        for(auto i=nums.begin();i<nums.end()-1;i++)\n        {\n            if(*i==*(i+1))\n            {\n                nums.erase(i+1);\n                i--;\n            }\n        }\n        return nums.size();\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"remove-duplicates-from-sorted-array"}
